OL,3,CSix-month delay to next phase of Omagh
OL,4,CBombing Inquiry
OL,6,FThe next phase of hearings at the
OL,7,FOmagh Bombing Inquiry will take place
OL,8,Fsix months later than scheduled, the
OL,9,Flead counsel to the inquiry has said.
OL,11,FPublic hearings about the days
OL,12,Fimmediately before and after the 1998
OL,13,Fatrocity in the Co Tyrone town were
OL,14,Fdue to start on March 9 2026.
OL,16,FOn Thursday Paul Greaney KC said they
OL,17,Fwill now begin on September 21.
OL,19,FHe said the delay was due to material
OL,20,F"originating from the Republic of
OL,21,FIreland not being available".
