OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773936670
OL,3,CSix-month delay to next phase of Omagh
OL,4,CBombing Inquiry
OL,6,FMr Greaney said the volume of that
OL,7,Fmaterial should not be
OL,8,F"underestimated", adding that while it
OL,9,Fis being made available to the inquiry
OL,10,Fon a "rolling basis" it will only be
OL,11,Ffully disclosed by June.
OL,13,FHe said the inquiry legal team is
OL,14,F"acutely aware of how disappointing
OL,15,Fthis will be for many people".
